          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/36589911-the-lords-of-discipline">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6326169-negin?shelf=all-time-favourites">all-time-favourites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6326169-negin?shelf=usa">usa</a>
