          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16540144-soulsurvivor?shelf=favorite-books">favorite-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16540144-soulsurvivor?shelf=worth-your-consideration">worth-your-consideration</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16540144-soulsurvivor?shelf=highly-recommended">highly-recommended</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16540144-soulsurvivor?shelf=2020-to-reads">2020-to-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/16540144-soulsurvivor?shelf=as-soon-as-possible">as-soon-as-possible</a>, 
