<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/87202.The_Edge_of_Sadness"><img alt="The Edge of Sadness" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1347499598l/87202._SX98_.jpg" />
